  {
    "key": "KAN-3",
    "fields": {
      "summary": "Build Testing agent (writes \u0026 runs tests, loops back on fail)",
      "description": {
        "content": [
          {
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2,
              "localId": "ebd734dc741c"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Description",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "heading"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "localId": "cf4697c5b6d5"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Given a PR opened by the Junior Dev agent, write dedicated tests, run them, and on failure hand work back to the Junior agent.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "localId": "93220cdbbae4"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Three files to create:",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "- ",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ],
                "text": "agents/testing/prompt.md",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "- ",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ],
                "text": "agents/testing/README.md",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "- ",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ],
                "text": ".github/workflows/testing.yml",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "text": " — triggered on ",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ],
                "text": "pull_request",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "text": " events filtered to the Junior agent's branch naming pattern (see open questions below); loop-back has a hard cap to prevent infinite ping-pong",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2,
              "localId": "77136aef9519"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Context",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "heading"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "localId": "a03bad2b9bae"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "The Testing agent is the automated quality gate on the easy path of the agentic workflow (",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ],
                "text": "docs/agentic-workflow.md",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "text": "). It keeps the Junior↔Testing loop fully autonomous — failures bounce inside the loop without involving a human. Blocked by KAN-2 (Junior Developer agent), which must define the branch naming pattern before this workflow can be wired up.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2,
              "localId": "ff5a33e8c714"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Acceptance Criteria",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "heading"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "localId": "1efe31f8b03e"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "attrs": {
                  "localId": "4120a76a7f89"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "attrs": {
                      "localId": "01474e83b037"
                    },
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "A deliberately-failing PR from the Junior agent produces tests, runs them, fails, and re-triggers the Junior agent exactly once.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "listItem"
              },
              {
                "attrs": {
                  "localId": "667a36cfd0f1"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "attrs": {
                      "localId": "3ddacdfd724d"
                    },
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "Run log committed under ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "marks": [
                          {
                            "type": "code"
                          }
                        ],
                        "text": ".github/agent-logs/testing/pr-\u003cn\u003e/\u003crun-id\u003e.json",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": ".",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "listItem"
              },
              {
                "attrs": {
                  "localId": "81d2b739b5c4"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "attrs": {
                      "localId": "9f49aa1f012f"
                    },
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "Hard cap prevents an infinite Junior↔Testing ping-pong.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "listItem"
              }
            ],
            "type": "bulletList"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2,
              "localId": "a7777b34cc20"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Needs human input",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "heading"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "localId": "82806b0b7282"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "attrs": {
                  "localId": "97a8e7b806d9"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "attrs": {
                      "localId": "a62c7588393e"
                    },
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "[ ] Which loop-back mechanism should the Testing agent use on failure: (A) post a structured PR comment that the Junior workflow watches for, or (B) set a label on the PR that re-triggers the Junior workflow?",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "listItem"
              },
              {
                "attrs": {
                  "localId": "e24e63a2efe2"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "attrs": {
                      "localId": "3997be5b9bf2"
                    },
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "text": "[ ] What branch naming pattern will the Junior Developer agent use for its PRs? (This determines the ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "marks": [
                          {
                            "type": "code"
                          }
                        ],
                        "text": "branches:",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " filter in ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "marks": [
                          {
                            "type": "code"
                          }
                        ],
                        "text": "testing.yml",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " — to be decided in KAN-2 and referenced here.)",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "listItem"
              }
            ],
            "type": "bulletList"
          }
